Class CommonContact

  • entity.CommonContact
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bean, com.guidewire.pl.domain.contact.CommonContactAdapter

    public class CommonContact
implements Bean, com.guidewire.pl.domain.contact.CommonContactAdapter, com.guidewire.pl.domain.contact.CommonContactAdapter
    This is a shared delegate/interface which allows code to operate on those common properties held by either Contact or ABContact entities. This allows code-sharing in cases where code might be used by both ContactManager and another Guidewire application.
